						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the left wall of the main entrance of the same temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Ānanda, Mārgaśira ba. 5.</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a monetary transaction between Gutti Tirumala Nāyaka and Koṇidela Chainna-kṛishṇama-Nāyaka on one side and Vōbaya, son of Chinnamaseṭṭi on the other.</p>						

						</summary>
